               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>A portion of the first thousand of <title xml:lang="ta">Tivviyappirapantam</title> (NTP 1-871).</p>
<p>The additional title-page (U1) erroneously states that the bundle contains the <foreign xml:lang="ta">tiruvāymoḻi mutal āyiram</foreign> (the <title xml:lang="ta">Tiruvāymoḻi</title> is the 4th thousand).</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (March 2023).</p>      
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      

</summary>
                  
